        <h5 class="post_author"><a class="author" href="/bestbisidea" data-from-id="-51675727" data-post-id="-51675727_36767">Идеи малого бизнеса</a> <span class="explain"><IDXSKIP><span class="wall_fixed_label">&nbsp;запись закреплена</span></IDXSKIP></span></h5>
        <div class="post_date"><a  class="post_link"  href="/wall-51675727_36767"  onclick="return showWiki({w: 'wall-51675727_36767'}, false, event);" ><span class="rel_date">29 мар 2016</span></a></div>
