<div id=\"wpt-51675727_36688\" class=\"_wall_post_cont\"><div class=\"wall_post_text\">Соучредитель холдинга Ginza Project Вадим Лапин расскажет о том, как на регулярной основе открывать успешные рестораны.<\/div><div class=\"page_post_sized_thumbs  clear_fix\" style=\"width: 510px; height: 286px;\"><a href=\"\/video-51675727_456239064?list=35ac9ee0a127c12283\" data-video=\"-51675727_456239064\" data-list=\"35ac9ee0a127c12283\" data-duration=\"1381\" aria-label=\"видеозапись ИСКУССТВО БИЗНЕСА: ресторанного бизнеса\" onclick=\"return showInlineVideo('-51675727_456239064', '35ac9ee0a127c12283', {autoplay: 1, addParams: { post_id: '-51675727_36688' }}, event, this);\" style=\"width: 510px; height: 287px; background-image: url(https:\/\/pp.vk.me\/c629120\/u36593467\/video\/x_b4ae6d61.jpg)\" class=\"page_post_thumb_wrap image_cover  page_post_thumb_video page_post_thumb_last_column page_post_thumb_last_row\"><div class=\"page_post_video_play_inline\"><\/div><div class=\"page_wm\"><\/div><div class=\"page_post_video_duration_single\">23:01<\/div><\/a><\/div><div class=\"media_desc post_video_desc\">\n  <a class=\"lnk\" id=\"post_media_lnk-51675727_36688_0\"  onclick=\"return showVideo('-51675727_456239064', '35ac9ee0a127c12283', {autoplay: 1, queue: 1, addParams: { post_id: '-51675727_36688' }}, event);\"  href=\"\/video-51675727_456239064?list=35ac9ee0a127c12283\" data-video=\"-51675727_456239064\" data-list=\"35ac9ee0a127c12283\" data-duration=\"1381\" aria-label=\"видеозапись ИСКУССТВО БИЗНЕСА: ресторанного бизнеса\">\n    <div class=\"a post_video_title\">ИСКУССТВО БИЗНЕСА: ресторанного бизнеса<\/div><div class=\"post_video_views_count\">4<span class=\"num_delim\"> <\/span>091 просмотр<\/div>\n  <\/a>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n        <div class=\"post_full_like_wrap clear_fix\">\n  <div class=\"post_full_like\">\n    <a href=\"#\" class=\"post_like _like_wrap \" onmouseover=\"Wall.likesShow(this, '-51675727_36688')\" onclick=\"return Wall.likeIt(this, '-51675727_36688'